  stimulus_text = 'The new museum, __ a collection of artifacts from around the world, is set to open next month. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
